snippet.title: “She was a good lay” James Franco Forced to appear in court over alleged Amber Heard Affair
snippet.description:
James Franco must appear in court over alleged Amber Heard Affair

James Franco's problems just keep piling up.

Franco has been served in the long-running court dispute between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, after sparking controversy by revealing he slept with his students.

Franco, 43, will be questioned about his involvement with Heard while she was still married to Depp.

Lawyers for Depp want to know if the actor observed the alleged injuries on Heard's face.

Franco will take the deposition in Depp's $50 million defamation case against Heard early next year.

Depp is suing Heard in Virginia over an op-ed she published in the Washington Post in 2018 in which she recounted being a victim of domestic abuse. She didn't identify her ex, but he believes she was referring to him as her abuser. Depp denies any wrongdoing.
